{"tid":2385372,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"江嘉敏網店賣贈品 被寸等錢使","createTime":"2021-01-29T04:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T03:17:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"875e3a8261c5ea4da4778a6ba3698cc345e28587","tid":2385372,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/03Ls7Cxo2E3MC8a0Px47Gw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Z1MEMFxGzNuvE9SjQBy7Kw--~B/aD01NDA7dz01NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/thesun.hk.com/7598b22dbcf53333d77f975e26e6f7f3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F03Ls7Cxo2E3MC8a0Px47Gw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZ1MEMFxGzNuvE9SjQBy7Kw--~B%2FaD01NDA7dz01NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F7598b22dbcf53333d77f975e26e6f7f3&h=91634f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江嘉敏與友人搞了一個網店出售二手物品，目的是鼓勵環保及做慈善，卻引來不少網友質疑，指她出售公關贈品扮環保，揶揄她「究竟有幾等錢使」，更質疑所籌得的款項會怎樣捐出和捐去哪個機構。<br />\n<br />\n就網友質疑，江嘉敏在社交網回應：「鑑於最近有人惡意抹黑和中傷，我覺得有必要解釋清楚！物品在Story中有說明有些是客戶送的禮物。」至於收入去向，她解釋：「有公開網上討論究竟捐給甚麼機構和人才是最好的。」最後她再次強調：「網店是環保慈善用途的，不是用來賺錢！」"},{"pid":"f704adf329a6d1441a0d0591423b751de48847d9","tid":2385372,"uid":52605,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:05:05.000Z","msg":"MK格同臭閪味出曬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea48f4c866cd00ef17b728062baff891cc3125d","tid":2385372,"uid":358691,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"好cheap <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d1920268f0d8b5617c097f3fef295ffbc0d9a9","tid":2385372,"uid":58880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"賣相仲好賺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gi